3111	// Lode, divine-enumerate to confirm it appears, divine-inspect to confirm the
3112	// member tags + vouch envelope rode in, banish the whole Lode, then divine-
3113	// enumerate to confirm the registry is restored. Parallel to hallmark-lifecycle
3114	// on the made side. Requires a reliquary yoked on the busybox vessel (same
3115	// precondition hallmark-lifecycle's ordain carries).
